overview: Rassvet presents I MISSED YOU  Featuring Val Bauer, Tolya Titaev, Cambryan Sedlick, Patrick Franklin, Yaroslav Kondratiev, Igor smirnov, Lilian Fev, Alix Malnati & Joseph Biais.  Filmed and edited by Trevor Dare during 2021 in Mexico City, Los Angeles, Moscow and Paris.  Additional Filming by Ryan Lee, James Cruickshank and Romain Batard.  RASSVET 2022.
title: "I Missed You"
